一维无限长均匀弹性弦的横向微幅振动是由二阶线性波动方程描述的：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\left(\frac{\partial^{2}}{\partial t^{2}}-a^{2}\frac{\partial^{2}}{\partial x^{2}}\right)u=0\qquad(x,t)\in(-\infty,\infty)\times(0,\infty)\label{eq:微分方程：双曲型：双波}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

相应的初始条件由初始位移和初始速度共同构成：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
u(x,t=0)=u_{0}(x)\qquad\frac{\partial u(x,t=0)}{\partial t}=v_{0}(x)\label{eq:微分方程：双曲型：双波：初值}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Solution*
方程 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:微分方程：双曲型：双波"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 中的二阶微分算符可以分解为两个一阶微分算符的乘积：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial^{2}}{\partial t^{2}}-a^{2}\frac{\partial^{2}}{\partial x^{2}}=\left(\frac{\partial}{\partial t}-a\frac{\partial}{\partial x}\right)\left(\frac{\partial}{\partial t}+a\frac{\partial}{\partial x}\right)
\]

\end_inset

引入坐标变换
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{bmatrix}\xi\\
\eta
\end{bmatrix}\coloneqq\begin{bmatrix}x+at\\
x-at
\end{bmatrix}\implies\begin{bmatrix}\partial_{t}\\
\partial_{x}
\end{bmatrix}=\begin{bmatrix}\partial_{t}\xi & \partial_{t}\eta\\
\partial_{x}\xi & \partial_{x}\eta
\end{bmatrix}\begin{bmatrix}\partial_{\xi}\\
\partial_{\eta}
\end{bmatrix}=\begin{bmatrix}a & -a\\
1 & 1
\end{bmatrix}\begin{bmatrix}\partial_{\xi}\\
\partial_{\eta}
\end{bmatrix}
\]

\end_inset

只要该变换是非退化的，即 
\begin_inset Formula $a\ne0$
\end_inset

，就有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{bmatrix}\partial_{t}-a\partial_{x}\\
\partial_{t}+a\partial_{x}
\end{bmatrix}=\begin{bmatrix}1 & -a\\
1 & +a
\end{bmatrix}\begin{bmatrix}\partial_{t}\\
\partial_{x}
\end{bmatrix}=\begin{bmatrix} & -2a\\
2a
\end{bmatrix}\begin{bmatrix}\partial_{\xi}\\
\partial_{\eta}
\end{bmatrix}
\]

\end_inset

于是可以将方程 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:微分方程：双曲型：双波"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 化为标准形式 (canonical form)：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\partial_{\xi}\partial_{\eta}u=0
\]

\end_inset

它的通解为：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u(x,t)=f(\xi)+g(\eta)=f(x+at)+g(x-at)
\]

\end_inset

其中 
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

 与 
\begin_inset Formula $g$
\end_inset

 可以是任何一阶可微的一元函数。代入初始条件 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:微分方程：双曲型：双波：初值"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 可以定出 
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

 与 
\begin_inset Formula $g$
\end_inset

，从而得到原初值问题的解：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u(x,t)=\frac{u_{0}(x+at)+u_{0}(x-at)}{2}+\int_{x-at}^{x+at}\frac{v_{0}(\zeta)}{2a}\dd{\zeta}
\]

\end_inset

它表示两个独立的（线性）波分别以速度 
\begin_inset Formula $\pm a$
\end_inset

 沿 
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

 方向运动。
\end_layout

