，使其满足常系数线性偏微分方程组：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\left(\frac{\partial}{\partial t}+\underline{A}\,\frac{\partial}{\partial x}\right)\vert U\rangle=\vert0\rangle\qquad(x,t)\in(-\infty,\infty)\times(t_{0},\infty)\label{eq:微分方程：双曲型：多波：线性}
\end{equation}

