\underline{A}=\begin{bmatrix}A_{11} & \cdots & A_{1n}\\
\vdots &  & \vdots\\
A_{n1} & \cdots & A_{nn}
\end{bmatrix}\in\mathbb{R}^{n\times n}\qquad\vert U(x,t)\rangle=\begin{bmatrix}U_{1}(x,t)\\
\vdots\\
U_{n}(x,t)
\end{bmatrix}
\]

\end_inset

及对 
