\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
若 
\begin_inset Formula $\underline{A}$
\end_inset

 有 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

 个互异的实特征值 
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{1}<\cdots<\lambda_{n}$
\end_inset

，则称该方程组为（沿 
\begin_inset Formula $t$
\end_inset

 轴）严格双曲型的 (strictly hyperbolic)。
