\begin_layout Itemize
若 
\begin_inset Formula $\underline{A}$
\end_inset

 有 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

 个实特征值 
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{1}\le\cdots\le\lambda_{n}$
\end_inset

，且有 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

 个线性无关的特征向量，则称该方程组为（沿 
