caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 的解为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\boxed{\vert U(x,t)\rangle=\sum_{i=1}^{n}\vert R_{i}\rangle\langle L_{i}\vert U_{0}(x-\lambda_{i}\cdot(t-t_{0}))\rangle}\qquad(x,t)\in(-\infty,\infty)\times[t_{0},\infty)
