\begin_layout Proof
\begin_inset Formula $\vert U\rangle$
\end_inset

 的初值（式 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:微分方程：双曲型：多波：初值"

\end_inset

）可以化为 
\begin_inset Formula $\vert V\rangle$
