\end_inset

 个独立的单波初值问题。代入式 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:微分方程：双曲型：单波：线性：光滑解"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 即得这 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

 个单波的解：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
V_{i}(x,t)=\langle L_{i}\vert U_{0}(x-\lambda_{i}\cdot(t-t_{0}))\rangle\qquad i=1,\dots,n
\]

\end_inset

原初值问题 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "prob:微分方程：双曲型：多波：线性"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 的解是这些单波的线性组合：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}\vert U(x,t)\rangle & =\underbrace{\underline{L}^{-1}}_{\underline{R}}\,\vert V(x,t)\rangle=\begin{bmatrix}\vert R_{1}\rangle & \cdots & \vert R_{n}\rangle\end{bmatrix}\begin{bmatrix}V_{1}(x,t)\\
\vdots\\
V_{n}(x,t)
\end{bmatrix}\\
 & =\sum_{i=1}^{n}\vert R_{i}\rangle\underbrace{\langle L_{i}\vert U_{0}(x-\lambda_{i}\cdot(t-t_{0}))\rangle}_{V_{i}(x,t)}
