\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(\frac{\partial}{\partial t}+\lambda\frac{\partial}{\partial x}\right)U=0\qquad\lambda\in\mathbb{R}
\]

\end_inset

即以 
\begin_inset Formula $F(U)\coloneqq\lambda U$
